it becomes so hot
that anything that touches it will
instantly go
up in flames.

devastating move.
It rubs its blaz­
 ing fur together

flavor_text_entries.crystal:
When heat from its
body causes the
air around it to shimmer, this is a
sign that it is
ready to battle.
flavor_text_entries.ruby:
TYPHLOSION obscures itself behind a
shimmering heat haze that it creates
using its intensely hot flames. This POKéMON creates blazing explosive
blasts that burn everything to cinders.
